- Right.</font>

63
00:04:14,670 --> 00:04:17,419
<font size="24">[ ROARING ]</font>

64
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:22,259
<font size="24">- [ SHOUTING ]
- [ ROARING ]</font>

65
