204
00:13:01,650 --> 00:13:04,149
<font size="24">It's not home,
but it'll do just fine.</font>

205
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,159
<font size="24">What a lovely bed.</font>

206
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,579
<font size="24">- Got ta.
- [ SNIFFS ] I found some cheese.</font>

207
00:13:08,660 --> 00:13:11,159
<font size="24">- Ow! [ GRUNTS ]
- Blah! Awful stuff.</font>

208
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:15,499
<font size="24">- Is that you, Gorder?
- How did you know?</font>

209
00:13:15,580 --> 00:13:18,499
<font size="24">Enough!
What are you doing in my house?</font>

210
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:20,499
<font size="24">[ GRUNTS ] Hey!</font>

211
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:23,219
<font size="24">- [ SNICKERS ]
- Oh, no, no, no.</font>

212
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:26,889
<font size="24">- Dead broad off the table.
