213
00:13:26,970 --> 00:13:30,139
<font size="24">Huh? [ GASPS ]</font>

214
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:32,849
<font size="24">[ MALE VOICE ] What?</font>

215
00:13:32,930 --> 00:13:37,689
<font size="24">I live in a swamp. I put up signs.
I'm a terrifying ogre!</font>

216
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:40,399
