241
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:55,469
<font size="24">- Any one at all?
- Me! Me!</font>

242
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:57,479
<font size="24">- Anyone?
- Oh! Oh, pick me!</font>

243
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:59,979
<font size="24">Oh, I know! I know! Me, me!</font>

244
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:03,189
<font size="24">[ SIGHS ] Okay, fine.</font>

245
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:07,819
<font size="24">Attention,
all fairy tale things.</font>

246
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:12,619
<font size="24">Do not get comfortable.
