249
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:24,129
<font size="24">[ CHEERING ]</font>

250
00:15:24,210 --> 00:15:27,089
<font size="24">- [ TWITTERING ]
- [ CHEERING CONTINUES ]</font>

251
00:15:27,170 --> 00:15:30,129
<font size="24">Oh! You!</font>

252
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:32,139
<font size="24">You're coming with me.</font>

253
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:34,559
<font size="24">All right, that's
what I like to hear, man.</font>

254
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:38,429
<font size="24">Shrek and Donkey, two stalwart friends,
