255
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:40,519
<font size="24">I love it!</font>

256
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:43,769
<font size="24">♪ - On the road again Sing it ♪
♪ with me, Shrek. - Hey. Oh, oh! ♪</font>

257
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,819
<font size="24">♪ I can't wait to get ♪
♪ on the road again ♪</font>

258
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:47,819
<font size="24">What did I say about singing?</font>

259
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:49,819
<font size="24">- Can I whistle?
- No.</font>

260
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:52,699
<font size="24">- Can I hum it?
- All right, hum it.</font>

261
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:57,659
<font size="24">♪ [ HUMMING ] ♪</font>

