00:16:25,610 --> 00:16:29,229
<font size="24">[ COUGHING ]</font>

266
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:33,239
<font size="24">[ LAUGHING ]</font>

267
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:36,829
<font size="24">[ CLEARS THROAT ]</font>

268
00:16:38,450 --> 00:16:40,909
<font size="24">Run, run, run,
