280
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:20,079
<font size="24">Yes, I know the muffin man,
who lives on Drury Lane?</font>

281
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:23,579
<font size="24">Well, she's married
to the muffin man.</font>

282
00:17:23,660 --> 00:17:25,789
<font size="24">- The muffin man?
