00:17:58,570 --> 00:18:00,449
<font size="24">Mirror, mirror, on the wall.</font>

292
00:18:00,530 --> 00:18:03,909
<font size="24">Is this not the most
perfect kingdom of them all?</font>

293
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,579
<font size="24">Well, technically
