304
00:18:43,330 --> 00:18:45,699
<font size="24">Please welcome Cinderella.</font>

305
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:49,829
<font size="24">Bachelorette number two is a cape-wearing
girl from the land of fancy.</font>

306
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:52,629
