340
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:34,149
<font size="24">Hey, wait. Wait up, Shrek.</font>

341
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:37,109
<font size="24">Hurry, darling.
We're late. Hurry.</font>

342
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:42,239
<font size="24">- Hey, you!
- [ SCREAMS ]</font>

343
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:45,159
<font size="24">Wait a second.
Look, I'm not gonna eat ta.</font>

344
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:49,159
<font size="24">- I just... I just...
- [ WHIMPERING ]</font>

345
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,329
<font size="24">[ SIGHS ]</font>

346
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:55,579
<font size="24">[ WHIMPERING, GROANS ]</font>

347
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:05,259
<font size="24">[ TURNSTILE CLATTERS ]</font>

348
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,759
