<font size="24">♪ Please keep off of the grass ♪
♪ Shine your shoes, wipe your... face ♪</font>

363
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:08,989
<font size="24">♪ DuLoc is, DuLoc is ♪</font>

364
00:22:09,070 --> 00:22:12,539
<font size="24">♪ DuLoc is a perfect ♪</font>

365
00:22:12,620 --> 00:22:16,039
<font size="24">♪ - Place ♪
♪ - [ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ] ♪</font>

366
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:18,709
<font size="24">[ WHIRRING ]</font>

367
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:24,009
<font size="24">Wow! Let's do that again!</font>

