Why don't you just go ask her?</font>

1222
01:13:59,180 --> 01:14:02,189
<font size="24">The wedding!
We'll never make it in time.</font>

1223
01:14:02,270 --> 01:14:05,479
<font size="24">Ha-ha-ha! Never fear, for where
there's a will, there's a way,</font>

1224
01:14:05,570 --> 01:14:07,689
<font size="24">and I have a way. [ WHISTLES ]</font>

1225
01:14:12,070 --> 01:14:14,529
<font size="24">- Donkey?
- [ DONKEY LAUGHING ]</font>

1226
01:14:14,620 --> 01:14:16,989
<font size="24">I guess it's just
my animal magnetism.</font>

1227
01:14:17,080 --> 01:14:20,249
<font size="24">[ LAUGHING ] Aw, come here, you.</font>

1228
01:14:20,330 --> 01:14:23,129
<font size="24">All right, all right. Don't get
all slobbery. No one likes a kiss ass.</font>

1229
