1234
01:15:01,000 --> 01:15:03,539
<font size="24">People of DuLoc,</font>

1235
01:15:03,620 --> 01:15:06,289
<font size="24">we gather here today...</font>

1236
01:15:06,380 --> 01:15:08,419
