1237
01:15:08,500 --> 01:15:10,419
<font size="24">- to the union...
- Um...</font>

1238
01:15:10,510 --> 01:15:12,969
<font size="24">- Of our new king...
- Excuse me.</font>

1239
01:15:13,050 --> 01:15:15,719
<font size="24">- Could we just skip ahead to the I do's?
- [ CHUCKLING ]</font>

1240
01:15:15,800 --> 01:15:17,719
