1247
01:15:42,200 --> 01:15:43,909
<font size="24">Wait. What are you doing?
Listen to me!</font>

1248
01:15:44,000 --> 01:15:45,919
<font size="24">- Look, you love this woman, don't you?
- Yes.</font>

1249
01:15:46,000 --> 01:15:47,289
<font size="24">- You wanna hold her?
- Yes.</font>

1250
01:15:47,380 --> 01:15:49,589
<font size="24">- Please her?
- Yes!</font>

1251
